02:50:00,600 --> 02:50:17,200
<i><font color="#89B4FA">♫ Yéni ve lintë yuldar avánier</font></i>
<i><font color="#F9E2AF">(The long years have passed like swift draughts)</font></i>

229
02:50:18,600 --> 02:50:40,200
<i><font color="#89B4FA">♫ mi oromardi lissë-miruvóreva</font></i>
<i><font color="#F9E2AF">(of the sweet mead in lofty halls)</font></i>

230
02:50:48,410 --> 02:50:50,909
<font color="#A6E3A1">Am meleth dîn...</font>
<font color="#F9E2AF">(For her love...)</font>

231
02:50:50,910 --> 02:50:57,109
<font color="#A6E3A1">I ant e guil Arwen Undómiel pígatha.</font>
<font color="#F9E2AF">(The gift of life of Arwen will dwindle.)</font>

232
02:50:57,110 --> 02:51:02,009
<font color="#A6E3A1">Aníron i e broniatha, ad ae periatham...</font>
<font color="#F9E2AF">(I wish that she endures, even if we separate...)</font>

233
02:51:02,010 --> 02:51:06,710
<font color="#A6E3A1">athar i methid en-amar hen.</font>
<font color="#F9E2AF">(beyond the limits of this world.)</font>

234
02:51:06,900 --> 02:51:12,690
<font color="#A6E3A1">Aníron i e círatha na Valannor.</font>
<font color="#F9E2AF">(I wish that she sails to Valinor.)</font>

235
02:51:37,610 --> 02:51:41,010
<font color="#89B4FA">Namárië.</font>
<font color="#F9E2AF">(Farewell.)</font>

236
02:51:43,010 --> 02:51:48,310
<font color="#A6E3A1">Nadath nâ i moe cerich.</font>
<font color="#F9E2AF">(There is much you have yet to do.)</font>

237
02:51:48,510 --> 02:51:57,619
<font color="#A6E3A1">Dan, ú-'eveditham, Elessar.</font>
<font color="#F9E2AF">(We shall not meet again, Elessar.)</font>

238
02:51:57,900 --> 02:52:32,200
<i><font color="#89B4FA">♫ Namárië! Nai hiruvalyë Valimar!</font></i>
<i><font color="#F9E2AF">(Farewell! Maybe thou shalt find Valimar!)</font></i>

239
02:52:32,900 --> 02:52:39,200
<i><font color="#89B4FA">♫ Namá[rië]!</font></i>
<i><font color="#F9E2AF">(Farewell!)</font></i>

240
02:56:43,970 --> 02:56:59,459
<i><font color="#89B4FA">♫ Et Eärello Endorenna utúlien</font></i>
<i><font color="#F9E2AF">(Out of the Great Sea to Middle-earth I come)</font></i>

241
02:57:00,970 --> 02:57:10,459
<i><font color="#89B4FA">♫ Sinomë maruvan ar Hildinyar</font></i>
<i><font color="#F9E2AF">(In this place I will abide, and my heirs)</font></i>

242
03:01:05,469 --> 03:01:08,118
<font color="#F38BA8">Gûm-ishi...</font>
<font color="#F9E2AF">(In the void...)</font>

243
03:01:13,734 --> 03:01:14,900
<font color="#F38BA8">...ashi...</font>
<font color="#F9E2AF">(...only...)</font>

244
03:01:17,250 --> 03:01:19,069
<font color="#F38BA8">...gurum</font>
<font color="#F9E2AF">(...death)</font>

245
03:02:33,390 --> 03:02:40,890
<font color="#F38BA8">Akha gûm-ishi ashi gurum</font>
<font color="#F9E2AF">(Here in the void, only death)</font>

246
03:03:12,233 --> 03:03:23,900
<i><font color="#89B4FA">♫ I tuo i macil a staldaron</font></i>
<i><font color="#F9E2AF">(The strength, the weapon, the needs of the valiant)</font></i>

247
03:03:24,233 --> 03:03:32,200
<i><font color="#89B4FA">♫ Marinyë Cor[ma]</font></i>
<i><font color="#F9E2AF">(Let the Ring be your weapon)</font></i>

248
03:03:32,233 --> 03:03:45,200
<i><font color="#89B4FA">♫ I tuo i macil a lelyat túrenna</font></i>
<i><font color="#F9E2AF">(The strength, the weapon, go to victory!)</font></i>

249
03:06:40,000 --> 03:06:55,000
<i><font color="#F38BA8">♫ Ash Burz-Durbagu burzum-ishi</font></i>
<i><font color="#F9E2AF">(One for the Dark Lord on his dark throne)</font></i>

250
03:07:58,970 --> 03:08:16,459
<i><font color="#A6E3A1">♫ Ú-velin i vegil an aegas</font></i>
<i><font color="#F9E2AF">(I do not love the bright sword for its sharpness)</font></i>

251
03:08:16,970 --> 03:08:38,459
<i><font color="#A6E3A1">♫ Egor i... bilin a linn[as]</font></i>
<i><font color="#F9E2AF">(Nor the... arrow for its swiftness)</font></i>

252
03:08:48,233 --> 03:09:00,200
<i><font color="#89B4FA">♫ I alda helda, i ehtelë lína</font></i>
<i><font color="#F9E2AF">(The tree is bare, the fountain still)</font></i>

253
03:09:01,233 --> 03:09:16,200
<i><font color="#89B4FA">♫ Manna lelyalye Voromírë?</font></i>
<i><font color="#F9E2AF">(Whither goest thou Boromir?)</font></i>

254
03:09:18,233 --> 03:09:35,200
<i><font color="#89B4FA">♫ Cánalya desse sí mas[së]</font></i>
<i><font color="#F9E2AF">(We heard your call but cannot find you)</font></i>

255
03:13:28,970 --> 03:13:50,459
<i><font color="#A6E3A1">♫ Ú-velin i ve[gil]</font></i>
<i><font color="#F9E2AF">(I do not love the bright sword)</font></i>

256
03:21:14,808 --> 03:21:20,365
<i>♫ Shines down upon you</i>

257
03:21:21,968 --> 03:21:28,032
<i>♫ May it be when darkness falls</i>

258
03:21:28,056 --> 03:21:34,625
<i>♫ Your heart will be true</i>

259
03:21:35,212 --> 03:21:41,387
<i>♫ You walk a lonely road</i>

260
03:21:41,411 --> 03:21:50,922
<i>♫ Oh! How far you are from home</i>

261
03:21:52,002 --> 03:22:03,585
<i><font color="#89B4FA">♫ Mornie utúlië</font></i>
<i><font color="#F9E2AF">(Darkness has come)</font></i>

262
03:22:03,609 --> 03:22:15,526
<i>♫ Believe and you will find your way</i>

263
03:22:15,550 --> 03:22:27,968
<i><font color="#89B4FA">♫ Mornie alantië</font></i>
<i><font color="#F9E2AF">(Darkness has fallen)</font></i>

264
03:22:27,992 --> 03:22:39,402
<i>♫ A promise lives within you now</i>

265
03:22:42,558 --> 03:22:48,609
<i>♫ May it be the shadow's call</i>

266
03:22:48,633 --> 03:22:54,086
<i>♫ Will fly away</i>

267
03:22:55,632 --> 03:23:01,537
<i>♫ May it be you journey on</i>

268
03:23:01,561 --> 03:23:06,927
<i>♫ To light the day</i>

269
03:23:08,066 --> 03:23:14,415
<i>♫ When the night is overcome</i>

270
03:23:14,439 --> 03:23:23,212
<i>♫ You may rise to find the sun</i>

271
03:23:23,402 --> 03:23:36,000
<i><font color="#89B4FA">♫ Mornie utúlië</font></i>
<i><font color="#F9E2AF">(Darkness has come)</font></i>

272
03:23:36,173 --> 03:23:47,753
<i>♫ Believe and you will find your way</i>

273
03:23:47,778 --> 03:23:59,532
<i><font color="#89B4FA">♫ Mornie alantië</font></i>
<i><font color="#F9E2AF">(Darkness has fallen)</font></i>

274
03:23:59,556 --> 03:24:11,965
<i>♫ A promise lives within you now</i>

275
03:24:11,991 --> 03:24:24,076
<i>♫ A promise lives within you...</i>

276
03:24:24,100 --> 03:24:31,400
<i>♫ ...now</i>

277
03:25:08,430 --> 03:25:14,835
<i>♫ When the cold of winter comes</i>

278
03:25:14,859 --> 03:25:21,206
<i>♫ Starless night will cover day</i>

279
03:25:21,230 --> 03:25:27,396
<i>♫ In the veiling of the sun</i>

280
03:25:27,420 --> 03:25:34,353
<i>♫ We will walk in bitter rain</i>

281
03:25:34,640 --> 03:25:39,676
<i>♫ But in dreams</i>

282
03:25:39,700 --> 03:25:46,670
<i>♫ I can hear your name</i>

283
03:25:46,694 --> 03:25:52,592
<i>♫ And in dreams</i>

284
03:25:52,616 --> 03:26:03,703
<i>♫ We will meet again</i>

285
03:26:22,376 --> 03:26:28,229
<i>♫ When the seas and mountains fall</i>

286
03:26:28,254 --> 03:26:34,946
<i>♫ And we come, to end of days</i>

287
03:26:34,970 --> 03:26:41,244
<i>♫ In the dark I hear a call</i>

288
03:26:41,268 --> 03:26:44,344
<i>♫ Calling me there</i>

289
03:26:44,765 --> 03:26:47,931
<i>♫ I will go there</i>

290
03:26:47,955 --> 03:26:53,115
<i>♫ And back again.</i>

291
03:26:53,139 --> 03:27:13,339
<i><font color="#A6E3A1">♫ A, Elbereth Gilthoniel</font></i>
<i><font color="#F9E2AF">(O, Elbereth Kindler of Stars)</font></i>

292
03:27:13,363 --> 03:27:35,025
<i><font color="#A6E3A1">♫ silivren penna míriel</font></i>
<i><font color="#F9E2AF">(Glittering light falling like shining jewels)</font></i>

